{"tid":551153,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼迷鬧爆！保羅普巴忽然變過街老鼠","createTime":"2018-02-05T11:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T20:45:20.000Z","uid":4661,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b49b6ad747440007ad7a4a24e09d1d646c31c1","tid":551153,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180205/photo/bkn-20180205145624245-0205_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180205185758\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180205%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180205145624245-0205_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180205185758&h=6c7cdeb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保羅普巴重返曼聯以來，原本人氣超高，而且隊友都好鍾意佢，不過佢疑似質疑領隊莫連奴嘅戰術後，日前喺紅魔主場以2:0擊敗哈特斯菲爾德嘅聯賽，罕有地被剔出正選陣容，傳媒同球迷都諗緊，到底佢係咪得罪咗寸王。更弊嘅係，賽前保羅普巴喺後備席上，竟然戴住頂帽同雙手插袋，迎接慕尼黑空難60周年嘅1分鐘默哀儀式，結果曼迷喺網上瘋狂批評佢冇教養，搞到佢忽然變成過街老鼠呀！"},{"pid":"47c89667a77957c8036ade9ae8f247e8e665d054","tid":551153,"uid":12154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"普巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d5f6f2dfadb14d38d548298b6cbb12c042d3f6","tid":551153,"uid":4586,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"神魔合一又關你咩事牙"},{"pid":"fe74126284469b83ea8c5ebc5092d72404ddba71","tid":551153,"uid":12660,"like":62,"dislike":4,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"無教養既人鬧人無教養 <br />\n可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8258eda68e9cd7eea3c28be5a5308961c60cf0","tid":551153,"uid":65406,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"魔性盡現。"},{"pid":"92edcc54954072b896df38046756edf0865e3ce9","tid":551153,"uid":13797,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20